show.description:
On her wedding day, Megha Shetty was left heartbroken when her husband Aditya rejected her, leaving a deep wound in her life.
Three years later, Aditya, now a successful CEO struggling with insomnia, contacts Megha for treatment through a friend’s recommendation.
Unaware of their shared past, they re-enter each other's lives.
With the help of their friends, their journey unfolds in a heartwarming and humorous way.
